<subSubSection lastPageId="5" lastPageNumber="702" pageId="4" pageNumber="701" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1127,1425,1610]" lastBlockId="5.[113,1089,220,340]" lastPageId="5" lastPageNumber="702" pageId="4" pageNumber="701">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,275,1425,1449]" pageId="4" pageNumber="701">Discussion.</emphasis>
The status of 
<taxonomicName authority="Ren &amp; Shi, 2006" authorityName="Ren &amp; Shi" authorityYear="2006" box="[417,848,1425,1450]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Indochillus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="701" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="convexigena">
<emphasis box="[417,671,1427,1450]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="701">Indochillus convexigena</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="REN G. - D. &amp; SHI A. - M." box="[676,848,1425,1449]" pageId="4" pageNumber="701" pagination="180 - 184" refId="ref2418" refString="REN G. - D. &amp; SHI A. - M. 2006: Two new record genera of Stenosini (Coleoptera, Tenebrionidae) from China, with descriptions of two new species. Acta Zootaxonomica Sinica 31: 180 - 184." type="journal article" year="2006">Ren &amp; Shi, 2006</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
was questioned by 
<bibRefCitation author="FOUQUE R." pageId="4" pageNumber="701" pagination="357 - 369" refId="ref2258" refString="FOUQUE R. 2008: Revision of the genus Pseudethas Fairmaire, with descriptions of four new species from Nepal and Thailand (Coleoptera: Tenebrionidae: Stenosini). Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde A, Neue Serie 1: 357 - 369." type="journal article" year="2008">FOUQUÉ (2008)</bibRefCitation>
. The species should be transferred to the subgenus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fairmaire" authorityYear="1896" box="[750,871,1459,1482]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Pseudethas" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="701" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[750,871,1459,1482]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="701">Pseudethas</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
of the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fairmaire" authorityYear="1896" box="[1006,1127,1459,1482]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Pseudethas" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="701" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1006,1127,1459,1482]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="701">Pseudethas</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on the following characters: elytral surface flattened, lateral margins of elytra parallelsided; base of elytra wider than pronotal base; epipleura of elytra with one row of punctures; males possessing small tooth on inner side of meso- and metatibiae; tempora convex laterally behind eyes; shallow median depression present on disc of pronotum. The species is similar to 
<taxonomicName authority="Kaszab, 1978" authorityName="Kaszab" authorityYear="1978" box="[140,688,220,244]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Pseudethas" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="702" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ladakhensis" subGenus="Pseudethas">
<emphasis box="[140,261,221,244]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="702">Pseudethas</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[276,397,221,244]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="702">Pseudethas</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[413,539,221,244]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="702">ladakhensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="KASZAB Z. &amp; SCHAWALLER W. &amp; SKOPIN N. G." box="[544,688,220,244]" pageId="5" pageNumber="702" pagination="215 - 234" refId="ref2302" refString="KASZAB Z., SCHAWALLER W. &amp; SKOPIN N. G. 1978: Systematik und Okologie einiger Tenebrionidae aus Kashmir und Ladakh (Insecta: Coleoptera). Senckenbergiana Biologica 59: 215 - 234." type="journal article" year="1978">Kaszab, 1978</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation author="KASZAB Z. &amp; SCHAWALLER W. &amp; SKOPIN N. G." box="[702,904,220,244]" pageId="5" pageNumber="702" pagination="215 - 234" refId="ref2302" refString="KASZAB Z., SCHAWALLER W. &amp; SKOPIN N. G. 1978: Systematik und Okologie einiger Tenebrionidae aus Kashmir und Ladakh (Insecta: Coleoptera). Senckenbergiana Biologica 59: 215 - 234." type="journal article" year="1978">KASZAB et al. 1978</bibRefCitation>
), but differs from the latter as follows: punctures of pronotum sparser; humeral angles of elytra rounded and not expending outwards; and antennae being more slender.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
